---
description: Never add Cursor as git co-author on kramli-cli commits
alwaysApply: true
---

Do **not** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` (or any Cursor/cursoragent trailer) to commit messages in this repository.

All commits should list only the human author unless another real collaborator explicitly co-authored the work.

This repo ships `.githooks/commit-msg` to strip accidental Cursor trailers; run `git config core.hooksPath .githooks` after clone.
